# Localisation (Paraglide.js)

## Supported languages

`en` (English), `fr` (Français), `ja` (日本語), `ru` (Русский), `zh` (中文)

## Rule: all user-facing strings must go through Paraglide

```svelte
<!-- ❌ Never hardcode strings -->
<p>All genres</p>
<button>Apply</button>

<!-- ✅ Use L -->
import { L } from '$lib'
<p>{L.home_all_genres()}</p>
<button>{L.common_apply()}</button>
```

## Adding a new key

**Must be added to ALL 5 files** at the same time:

```
messages/en.json  ← primary
messages/ru.json
messages/fr.json
messages/ja.json
messages/zh.json
```

Keys are snake_case. Example:

```json
// en.json
"home_all_statuses": "All statuses",

// ru.json
"home_all_statuses": "Все статусы",

// fr.json
"home_all_statuses": "Tous les statuts",

// ja.json
"home_all_statuses": "すべてのステータス",

// zh.json
"home_all_statuses": "全部状态",
```

## Parameterised strings

```json
"media_season_number": "Season {n}",
"common_by": "by {name}",
```

```svelte
{L.media_season_number({ n: season })}
{L.common_by({ name: author })}
```

## Country formatting

Never hardcode country names. Use `formatCountry` from `$shared/lib/labels`:

```svelte
import { formatCountry } from '$shared/lib/labels'
{formatCountry('US')}  // 🇺🇸 United States (or localised equivalent)
```

Flags are built via Unicode Regional Indicators (offset 127397), not emoji libraries.

## Watch status labels

```svelte
import { getWatchStatusLabels } from '$shared/lib/labels'
const watchStatusLabels = getWatchStatusLabels(L)
// { WATCHED: '...', IN_PROGRESS: '...', PLAN_TO_WATCH: '...' }
```
